<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>蛇环</strong></p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2020年1月2日</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/catthorns" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2171617); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2171617&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609636413" alt="CatThorns" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2171617)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/catthorns" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2171617); return false;">CatThorns</a></span></p>
<p>本文为<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/heavyblues" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2250250); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2250250&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609636413" alt="Heavyblues" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2250250)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/heavyblues" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2250250); return false;">Heavyblues</a></span>筹划设定“阿尔兹海默症”下作品。<br />
本文含有同性恋、自杀情节描写。</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+28</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
